ll]] \u2022 [[Tawera Kerr-Barlow]] \u2022 [[Anton Lienert-Brown]] \u2022 [[James Lowe (rugby union)|James Lowe]] \u2022 [[Damian McKenzie]] \u2022 [[Sam McNicol]] \u2022 [[Charlie Ngatai]] \u2022 [[Toni Pulu]] \u2022 [[Shaun Stevenson]] \u2022 [[Seta Tamanivalu]] \u2022 [[Latu Vaeno]] \u2022 [[Sam Vaka]] \u2022 [[Brad Weber]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Augustine Pulu]] \u2022 [[Chase Tiatia]] \u2022 [[Sonny Bill Williams]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Dave Rennie]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--------------- Crusaders squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Crusaders}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Michael Alaalatoa]] \u2022 [[Scott Barrett (rugby union)|Scott Barrett]] \u2022 [[Tim Boys]] \u2022 [[Wyatt Crockett]] \u2022 [[Owen Franks]] \u2022 [[Ben Funnell]] \u2022 [[Alex Hodgman]] \u2022 [[Joe Moody]] \u2022 [[Reed Prinsep]] \u2022 [[Kieran Read]] \u2022 [[Ged Robinson]] \u2022 [[Luke Romano]] \u2022 [[Pete Samu]] \u2022 [[Jordan Taufua]] \u2022 [[Codie Taylor]] \u2022 [[Matt Todd]] \u2022 [[Jimmy Tupou]] \u2022 [[Sam Whitelock]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Jed Brown]] \u2022 [[Mitchell Dunshea]] \u2022 [[Tim Perry (rugby union)|Tim Perry]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Ryan Crotty]] \u2022 [[Israel Dagg]] \u2022 [[Mitchell Drummond]] \u2022 [[Andrew Ellis|Andy Ellis]] \u2022 [[Kieron Fonotia]] \u2022 [[Leon Fukofuka]] \u2022 [[David Havili]] \u2022 [[Mitchell Hunt]] \u2022 [[Jone Macilai-Tori]] \u2022 [[Marty McKenzie (rugby union)|Marty McKenzie]] \u2022 [[Johnny McNicholl]] \u2022 [[Richie Mo'unga]] \u2022 [[Nemani Nadolo]] \u2022 [[Ben Volavola]] \u2022 [[Sea