Ando]] \u2022 [[Takuma Asahara]] \u2022 [[Tim Bond]] \u2022 [[Andrew Durutalo]] \u2022 [[Shota Horie]] \u2022 [[Yoshiya Hosoda]] \u2022 [[Keita Inagaki]] \u2022 [[Shinnosuke Kakinaga]] \u2022 [[Shokei Kin]] \u2022 [[Takeshi Kizu]] \u2022 [[Koo Ji-won]] \u2022 [[Naohiro Kotaki]] \u2022 [[Fa'atiga Lemalu]] \u2022 [[Tom\u00e1s Leonardi]] \u2022 [[Shinya Makabe (rugby union)|Shinya Makabe]] \u2022 [[Masataka Mikami]] \u2022 [[Liaki Moli]] \u2022 [[Futoshi Mori]] \u2022 [[Hitoshi Ono]] \u2022 [[Ed Quirk (rugby union)|Ed Quirk]] \u2022 [[Koki Yamamoto]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Ryuhei Arita]] \u2022 [[Shohei Hirano]] \u2022 [[Tsuyoshi Murata]] \u2022 [[Kazuhiko Usami]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Derek Carpenter]] \u2022 [[Atsushi Hiwasa]] \u2022 [[Daisuke Inoue (rugby union)|Daisuke Inoue]] \u2022 [[Kentaro Kodama]] \u2022 [[Viliami Lolohea]] \u2022 [[Mifiposeti Paea]] \u2022 [[Tusi Pisi]] \u2022 [[Yasutaka Sasakura]] \u2022 [[Kaito Shigeno]] \u2022 [[John Stewart (rugby union)|John Stewart]] \u2022 [[Yu Tamura]] \u2022 [[Harumichi Tatekawa]] \u2022 [[Riaan Viljoen]] \u2022 [[Akihito Yamada]] \u2022 [[Ryohei Yamanaka]] \u2022 [[Hajime Yamashita]] \u2022 [[Yuki Yatomi]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Mark Hammett]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--------------- Waratahs squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Waratahs}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Jack Dempsey (rugby union)|Jack Dempsey]] \u2022 [[Dave Dennis (rugby union)|Dave Dennis]] \u2022 [[Ned Hanigan]] \u2022 [[James Hilterbrand]] \u2022 [[Jed Holloway]] \u2022 [[Michael Hooper (rugby union)|Michael Hooper]] \u2022 [[Tolu Latu]] \u2022 [[Sam Lousi]] \u2022 [[Dean Mumm]] \u2022 [[Wycliff Palu]] \u2022 [[Tatafu Polota-Nau]] \u2022 [[Hugh Roach]] \u2022 [[Tom Robertson (rugby union)|Tom Robertson]] \u2022 [[Benn Robinson]] \u2022 [[Paddy Ryan (rugby union, born 1988)|Paddy Ryan]] \u2022 [[Will Skelton]] \u2022 [[Angus Ta'avao]] \u2022 [[Jeremy Tilse]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Ryan McCauley]] \u2022 [[Cameron Orr]] \u2022 [[Matt Sandell]] \u2022 [[Senio Toleafoa]] \u2022 [[Brad Wilkin]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Kurtley Beale]] \u2022 [[Matthew Carraro]] \u2022 [[Israel Folau]] \u2022 [[Bernard Foley]] \u2022 [[Zac Guildford]] \u2022 [[Bryce Hegarty]] \u2022 [[Rob Horne]] \u2022 [[David Horwitz]] \u2022 [[Andrew Kellaway (rugby union)|Andrew Kellaway]] \u2022 [[Matt Lucas (rugby union)|Matt Lucas]] \u2022 [[Taqele Naiyaravoro]] \u2022 [[Nick Phipps (rugby union)|Nick Phipps]] \u2022 [[Reece Robinson]] \u2022 [[Jim Stewart (rugby union)|Jim Stewart]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Henry Clunies-Ross]] \u2022 [[Andrew Deegan]] \u2022 [[Jake Gordon]] \u2022 [[Harry Jones (rugby union, born 1995)|Harry Jones]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Daryl Gibson]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n===Player statistics===\n\nThe top ten points scorers during the 2016 Super Rugby season are:<ref name=\"SA Rugby Top Scorers \u2013 2016 Vodacom Super Rugby\">{{SA Rugby Top Scorers | id=2714 | comp=2016 Vodacom Super Rugby | date=5 May 2016}}</ref>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable collapsible sortable\" style=\"text-align:center; width:60%;\"\n|-\n! colspan=\"100%\" | Top Ten points scorers\n|-\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | No\n! style=\"width:34%;\" | Player\n! style=\"width:30%;\" | Team\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | T\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | C\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | P\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | DG\n! style=\"width:6%;\"  | Pts\n<!-- Pos         ||              