ies squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Brumbies}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Robbie Abel]] \u2022 [[Allan Alaalatoa]] \u2022 [[Ben Alexander (rugby union)|Ben Alexander]] \u2022 [[Rory Arnold]] \u2022 [[Jarrad Butler]] \u2022 [[Sam Carter (rugby union)|Sam Carter]] \u2022 [[Blake Enever]] \u2022 [[Scott Fardy]] \u2022 [[Ben Hyne]] \u2022 [[Leslie Leulua\u2019iali\u2019i-Makin]] \u2022 [[Joshua Mann-Rea]] \u2022 [[Stephen Moore (rugby union)|Stephen Moore]] \u2022 [[David Pocock]] \u2022 [[Scott Sio]] \u2022 [[Jordan Smiler]] \u2022 [[Ruan Smith]] \u2022 [[Tom Staniforth]] \u2022 [[Ita Vaea]] \u2022 [[Michael Wells (rugby union)|Michael Wells]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Albert Anae]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Nigel Ah Wong]] \u2022 [[Robbie Coleman]] \u2022 [[Tom\u00e1s Cubelli]] \u2022 [[James Dargaville]] \u2022 [[Michael Dowsett]] \u2022 [[Jordan Jackson-Hope]] \u2022 [[Tevita Kuridrani]] \u2022 [[Christian Lealiifano]] \u2022 [[Joe Powell (rugby union)|Joe Powell]] \u2022 [[Andrew Smith (rugby union)|Andrew Smith]] \u2022 [[Henry Speight]] \u2022 [[Lausii Taliauli]] \u2022 [[Joe Tomane]] \u2022 [[Matt Toomua]] \u2022 [[Aidan Toua]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Nick Jooste]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Stephen Larkham]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--------------- Bulls squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Bulls}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards''