e]] \u2022 [[Dan Pryor]] \u2022 [[Mark Reddish]] \u2022 [[Aki Seiuli]] \u2022 [[Liam Squire]] \u2022 [[Joe Wheeler (rugby union)|Joe Wheeler]] \u2022 [[Luke Whitelock]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Jackson Hemopo]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Marty Banks]] \u2022 [[Jamie Booth]] \u2022 [[Jason Emery]] \u2022 [[Matt Faddes]] \u2022 [[Malakai Fekitoa]] \u2022 [[Waisake Naholo]] \u2022 [[Patrick Osborne (rugby player)|Patrick Osborne]] \u2022 [[Hayden Parker]] \u2022 [[Josh Renton]] \u2022 [[Aaron Smith (rugby union)|Aaron Smith]] \u2022 [[Ben Smith (rugby union)|Ben Smith]] \u2022 [[Fletcher Smith (rugby union)|Fletcher Smith]] \u2022 [[Lima Sopoaga]] \u2022 [[Fumiaki Tanaka]] \u2022 [[Rob Thompson (rugby union)|Rob Thompson]] \u2022 [[Te Aihe Toma]] \u2022 [[Ryan Tongia]] \u2022 [[Teihorangi Walden]] \u2022 [[Jack Wilson (rugby union)|Jack Wilson]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Richard Buckman]] \u2022 [[Sio Tomkinson]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Jamie Joseph]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--------------- Hurricanes squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Hurricanes}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Mark Abbott]] \u2022 [[Leni Apisai]] \u2022 [[Dane Coles]] \u2022 [[Geoffrey Cridge]] \u2022 [[Chris Eves]] \u2022 [[Michael Fatialofa]] \u2022 [[Vaea Fifita]] \u2022 [[Callum Gibbins]] \u2022 [[Reggie Goodes]] \u2022 [[Mike Kainga]] \u2022 [[Tony Lamborn]] \u2022 [[Motu Matu'u]] \u2022 [[Ben May (rugby union)|Ben May]] \u2022 [[Ricky Riccitelli]] \u2022 [[Ardie Savea]] \u2022 [[Brad Shields]] \u2022 [[Blade Thomson]] \u2022 [[Jeffery Toomaga-Allen]] \u2022 [[Loni Uhila]] \u