we]] \u2022 [[Jacques van Rooyen]] \u2022 [[Warren Whiteley]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[MB Lusaseni]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Backs'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[JW Bell]] \u2022 [[Marnitz Boshoff]] \u2022 [[Andries Coetzee]] \u2022 [[Ruan Combrinck]] \u2022 [[Ross Cronj\u00e9]] \u2022 [[Ashlon Davids]] \u2022 [[Faf de Klerk]] \u2022 [[Stokkies Hanekom]] \u2022 [[Rohan Janse van Rensburg]] \u2022 [[Elton Jantjies]] \u2022 [[Sylvian Mahuza]] \u2022 [[Lionel Mapoe]] \u2022 [[Koch Marx]] \u2022 [[Howard Mnisi]] \u2022 [[Jacques Nel]] \u2022 [[Courtnall Skosan]] \u2022 [[Dillon Smit]] \u2022 [[Jaco van der Walt]] \u2022 [[Anthony Volmink]] \u2022 [[Harold Vorster]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Sampie Mastriet]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Coach'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Johan Ackermann]]\n|}  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!--------------- Rebels squad ------------------>\n<div class=\"NavFrame collapsed\">\n  <div class=\"NavHead\">{{Rut Rebels}} squad</div>\n  <div class=\"NavContent\">\n{| cellpadding=\"2\" style=\"border: 1px solid white; font-size:90%;\"\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right;\" bgcolor=\"lavender\" | '''Forwards'''\n| style=\"text-align:left;\" | [[Cruze Ah-Nau]] \u2022 [[Steve Cummins]] \u2022 [[Colby Fainga'a]] \u2022 [[Scott Fuglistaller]] \u2022 [[Jamie Hagan]] \u2022 [[James Hanson (rugby union)|James Hanson]] \u2022 [[Sam Jeffries]] \u2022 [[Luke Jones (rugby union)|Luke Jones]] \u2022 [[Patrick Leafa]] \u2022 [[Rob Leota]] \u2022 [[Sean McMahon]] \u2022 [[Tim Metcher]] \u2022 [[Tom Moloney (rugby union)|Tom Moloney]] \u2022 [[Jordy Reid]] \u2022 [[Culum Retallick]] \u2022 [[Siliva Siliva]] \u2022 [[Toby Smith (rugby union)|Toby Smith]] \u2022 [[Adam Thomson (rugby union)|Adam Thomson]] \u2022 [[Lopeti Timani]] \u2022 [[Laurie Weeks (rugby)|Laurie Weeks]] \u2022 '''Did not play:''' \u2022 [[Ryan Cocker]] \u2022 [[Harley Fox]]\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:right